    History --------------------------------------------------------------

    Version 1.2 (21.04.96)
    À gvpscsi.device (and maybe also others)  had  problems  with  strange
      scsi sense lengths

    Version 1.1 (20.02.96)
    À should now  also  work with  scsi  devices  that don't  support fast
